=head1 DESCRIPTION

Provides information about a text extract in a chat response that can
be attributed to a source document.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 BeginOffset => Int

The zero-based location in the response string where the source
attribution starts.


=head2 EndOffset => Int

The zero-based location in the response string where the source
attribution ends.


=head2 MediaId => Str

The identifier of the media object associated with the text segment in
the source attribution.


=head2 MediaMimeType => Str

The MIME type (image/png) of the media object associated with the text
segment in the source attribution.


=head2 SnippetExcerpt => L<Paws::QBusiness::SnippetExcerpt>

The relevant text excerpt from a source that was used to generate a
citation text segment in an Amazon Q Business chat response.


=head2 SourceDetails => L<Paws::QBusiness::SourceDetails>

Source information for a segment of extracted text, including its media
type.



